{"type": "article", "id": 50131, "title": "麦当劳做了个巨无霸戒指，耐克冬奥广告片不错  | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-02-11T04:29:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 47725, "name": "狗年红包"}, {"id": 794, "name": "巨无霸"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180211120447mlVyeNRhkfI7nTFS.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/brand-marketing/why-lufthansa-decided-to-give-its-planes-a-new-paint-job/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>汉莎航空麾下 300 多架飞机将呈现新面貌</b></a>，这个“现代化的品牌形象”包括外圈变细的 Logo，去掉了黄色的深蓝机身涂装。汉莎还上线了一支短片，回顾过去一百年间的飞机涂装变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211113755kNnr6uvYJlyHsPoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.473034\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211113853TJQUy0aveq1wxPfr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.384375\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"https://nadineghosn.com/product/hamburger-ring\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦当劳在美国推出 #BlingMacContest 说出你对巨无霸的爱社交征集活动</b></a>，赢家可以获得一个镶满钻石 18K 金的 ? 巨无霸，还可以拆开来佩戴，价值 12,500 美元，真是有够夸张。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114332x8TSCOJadkqDjb9I.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.527586\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114241uQ5dmAGz7Ns9Tptq.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.550898\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211114308IPd13qZfMz6p2NsR.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.544258\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n0j_CX1S2es\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>冬奥会期间，Nike 伦敦发布了一支相当不错的广告《NOTHING BEATS A LONDONER》</b></a>，集结了三十多位运动员展现伦敦人的运动精神，在 YouTube 上的点击量超过了 1,197,752 次。创意依然由 W+K 负责。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b05511prw30&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=11&amp;v=KIMBR5ZMEvo\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>三星上线平昌冬奥会广告《Do what you can’t》</b></a>，一支中规中矩的正能量口号广告，这一主题是三星此前发布的品牌概念片的延续。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211115346YsL6wyQ30VPckgUJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.418750\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/43563.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>去年 10 月刚刚宣传成立的 CIA 中国独立创意联盟首次发布联合创意</b></a>。14 家创意热店都推出了自家设计的“狗年红包”，有的看起来还蛮有意思。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211120008k85VSePARgymGqwc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563725\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211120540TVOHYQEiWxp5A3MP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180211120614bqFM9sgzWRtOkC51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201802111206229x0UrFRmeOGhWENV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><div><strong>在国家版权局的推动下，腾讯音乐与网易云音乐就网络音乐版权达成合作，相互授权音乐作品，</strong>达到各自独家音乐作品数量的 99% 以上，并商定进行音乐版权长期合作。去年夏天，腾讯音乐和网易云音乐因版权纠纷互诉，各自被迫下架大量音乐作品。</div><p class=\"\">题图来源：麦当劳</p>"}